title: Cisco UCS: RAID Controller Operation Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/cisco
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check allows to monitor the operational status of
 the RAID controller in a Cisco UCS device. The check will report {OK} as long as the operational
 status is "operable", "removed" or "autoUpgrade". In other cases, the check will report
 a {WARNING} or {CRITICAL} status, based on the severity of the issue.

inventory:
 One service is created.
